updateBlades() - Method in class org.codehaus.griffon.jsilhouette.geom.Fan
Signals the fan to recalculate itself.
this is a convenience method to let a fan update itself when the properties of its prototype blade have been changed, it must be done manually as shapes are not guaranteed to be observable.
